, allowing them to pursue education based on merit, not wealth. The endowment ensures a lasting legacy of opportunity, empowering future generations to excel and contribute to society without the burden of overwhelming debt.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-1-8-billion-pivot-how-michael-bloombergs-historic-gift-rewrote-the-rules-of-college-access/articleshow/131034055.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/the-1-8-billion-pivot-how-michael-bloombergs-historic-gift-rewrote-the-rules-of-college-access/articleshow/131034055.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T18:34:53+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131038767,imgsize-174750.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[The $22 million mystery: Why a secret donor handed a small Canadian hospital the gift of a lifetime]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131034043.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A remarkable $22 million donation to Yarmouth Hospital Foundation in Nova Scotia has transformed local healthcare.  The anonymous donor's gift, intended for perpetual funding through investments, ensures over $1 million annually for patient benefits. This unprecedented act of generosity shifts focus from immediate needs to long-term planning, offering a powerful example of quiet philanthropy's lasting impact on regional communities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-22-million-mystery-why-a-secret-donor-handed-a-small-canadian-hospital-the-gift-of-a-lifetime/articleshow/131034043.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/the-22-million-mystery-why-a-secret-donor-handed-a-small-canadian-hospital-the-gift-of-a-lifetime/articleshow/131034043.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T18:33:21+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131040026,imgsize-1916929.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Kash Patel grilled over allegations of 'excessive drinking': 'If you want to pop bottles...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131066134.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kash-patel-grilled-at-us-senate-hearing-over-allegations-of-excessive-drinking-if-you-want-to-pop-bottles-stick-to-podcasting/articleshow/131066134.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/kash-patel-grilled-at-us-senate-hearing-over-allegations-of-excessive-drinking-if-you-want-to-pop-bottles-stick-to-podcasting/articleshow/131066134.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-13T18:12:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131066264,imgsize-119272.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Watch: Gunshots heard at Philippine Senate, lawmakers run for cover]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131065981.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gunshots-heard-at-philippine-senate-as-duterte-aide-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity-tries-to-evade-arrest-for-icc-trial-watch/articleshow/131065981.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/gunshots-heard-at-philippine-senate-as-duterte-aide-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity-tries-to-evade-arrest-for-icc-trial-watch/articleshow/1310659